OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1774534302
OL,3,CLyra McKee murder accused linked to
OL,4,Cscene by clothing and physical features
OL,6,FThree men accused of the murder of
OL,7,FLyra McKee have been linked to the
OL,8,Fscene by clothing and physical
OL,9,Ffeatures, a court has been told.
OL,11,FThe Belfast journalist, 29, died after
OL,12,Fbeing hit by a bullet as she stood
OL,13,Fclose to police vehicles while
OL,14,Fobserving rioting in the Creggan area
OL,15,Fof Londonderry on April 18 2019.
OL,17,FThe New IRA said it was responsible
OL,18,Ffor the killing.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
