PN,44702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1774534302
OL,3,CLyra McKee murder accused linked to
OL,4,Cscene by clothing and physical features
OL,6,FThree men from Derry ` Peter Cavanagh,
OL,7,F37, of Mary Street, Jordan Gareth
OL,8,FDevine, 25, of Bishop Street, and Paul
OL,9,FMcIntyre, 58, of Kells Walk ` have
OL,10,Fbeen charged with her murder.
OL,12,FThey are also facing other charges
OL,13,Fconnected to the shooting and the
OL,14,Frioting.
OL,16,FSix other Derry men are on trial on
OL,17,Fcharges including rioting and throwing
OL,18,Fpetrol bombs.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
