PN,44703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1774534302
OL,3,CLyra McKee murder accused linked to
OL,4,Cscene by clothing and physical features
OL,6,FThey are: Joseph Patrick Barr, 37, of
OL,7,FSandringham Drive, Jude Forest Coffey,
OL,8,F28, of Gartan Square, Joseph Anthony
OL,9,FCampbell, 25, of Gosheden Cottages,
OL,10,FPatrick Anthony Gallagher, 33, of John
OL,11,FField Place, Christopher Joseph
OL,12,FGillen, 45, of Balbane Pass, and
OL,13,FKieran George McCool, 57, of
OL,14,FBallymagowan Gardens.
OL,16,FAnother man accused of rioting and
OL,17,Fthrowing petrol bombs on the night of
OL,18,Fthe murder died during trial
OL,19,Fproceedings last year.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
