FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1774534302
OL,3,CLyra McKee murder accused linked to
OL,4,Cscene by clothing and physical features
OL,6,FIt is the prosecution's case that the
OL,7,Fthree men accused of murder had
OL,8,Faccompanied a lone gunman to the
OL,9,Ffiring point on the night, and had
OL,10,Fencouraged or assisted him.
OL,12,FThe trial opened in May 2024. In
OL,13,FFebruary, Judge Patricia Smyth
OL,14,Frejected a defence application that
OL,15,Fthere was no case to answer.
OL,17,FThe defendants filled the dock at
OL,18,FBelfast Crown Court on Wednesday
OL,19,Fmorning while the prosecution summed
OL,20,Fup their case against them.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
