FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1774534302
OL,3,CLyra McKee murder accused linked to
OL,4,Cscene by clothing and physical features
OL,6,FMs McKee's sister Nichola was among
OL,7,Fthose in the public gallery watching
OL,8,Fon.
OL,10,FProsecuting barrister David McDowell
OL,11,FKC said forensic image analyst Andrew
OL,12,FWooller identified 19 individuals by
OL,13,Fheight, build, clothing and trainers
OL,14,Fwho appeared to be involved in the
OL,15,Fdisorder.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
