FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1774534302
OL,3,CLyra McKee murder accused linked to
OL,4,Cscene by clothing and physical features
OL,6,FHe said Cavanagh, Devine and McIntyre,
OL,7,Fas well as Campbell and Gillen, can be
OL,8,Flinked to the scene on April 18 by an
OL,9,Fanalysis of imagery gathered, which
OL,10,Fincludes footage filmed by an MTV crew
OL,11,Fon the day of the shooting.
OL,13,FMr McDowell also contended that those
OL,14,Finvolved in rioting in the area on
OL,15,FApril 16 and 18 "displayed forensic
OL,16,Fawareness" by burning clothing.
OL,26,@wD@QOUxD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
