PN,44707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1774534302
OL,3,CLyra McKee murder accused linked to
OL,4,Cscene by clothing and physical features
OL,6,FHe noted a number of missing items of
OL,7,Fclothing associated with defendants
OL,8,Fthat were not discovered during
OL,9,Fsearches, nor have been produced
OL,10,Fsince, suggesting, he added, that they
OL,11,Fhad been "deliberately disposed of".
OL,13,FHe described this as an "important
OL,14,Fstrand in this case".
OL,16,FThe trial continues.
